{"tid":1876692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國家衛健委：治愈比例由1.3%上升到10.6%","createTime":"2020-02-12T14:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T01:30:45.000Z","uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"831eac2278bff9b964c12cc5cb1ea95fd9b8786d","tid":1876692,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"國家衛健委：治愈比例由1.3%上升到10.6%<br />\n<br />\n據@新華視點微博2月12日消息，國家衛生健康委員會新聞發言人米鋒12日在國務院聯防聯控機制新聞發布會上說，當前疫情形勢仍然十分嚴峻，但在一系列有力措施的推動下，疫情形勢總體上也出現一些積極變化。新增報告病例波動下降，新增確診病例數由最高時2月4日的3887例下降到2月11日的2015例，新增疑似病例數由最高時2月5日的5328例下降到2月11日的3342例，降幅分別達到了48.2%和37.3%；治愈出院人數較快增長，治愈比例由最低時1月27日的1.3%上升到2月11日的10.6%。"},{"pid":"d60c6b972bda41772a08ca3dfe9104ffce8230d1","tid":1876692,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae928f0b9a0f2d6b1fbcfb714b1d28b0431cd4dd","tid":1876692,"uid":345137,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"習種話要開工, 每日都係大奇蹟日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7beed2d265afbee614d1146d78a314cc3c78f742","tid":1876692,"uid":50386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:25:58.000Z","msg":"一系列<del>有力</del><span style=\"color: red;\">搬龍門</span>措施的推動下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52c437b42f3efc88644864f858c294b783122fc","tid":1876692,"uid":9315,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"路透社：習近平指遏制疫情措施衝過頭影響經濟<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508005-20200211.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508005-20200211.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=f01fc53c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/fram